Article: How Fashion Retailer H&M Is Betting On Artificial Intelligence And Big Data To Regain Profitability (forbes.com)

The article is about the Artificial Intelligence in the Fashion industry. H&M uses data from their consumers in their shops and online to understand their behaviours so they can predict what the market wants.

They use the supervised learning model to detect the trend and plan a flexible supply chain in order to have a high profitability (maximum of sales and they minimize the stocks).
